---
layout: base.njk
title: Writing
description: GTM intelligence, ICP methodology, and signal theory for B2B SaaS founders.
permalink: /blog/
---

{% set featuredPost = collections.featured[0] or collections.posts[0] %}

<section class="page-header">
  <div class="ph-inner inner">
    <p class="ph-ew">Writing</p>
    <h1 class="ph-hl">GTM intelligence and signal thinking for B2B SaaS.</h1>
    <p class="ph-sub">Read practical essays on ICP clarity, buyer-state dynamics, and evidence-led GTM decisions.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="filter-bar">
  <div class="fb-inner inner">
    <div class="fb-label">Filter by category</div>
    <div class="fb-actions">
      <button class="filter-btn is-active" data-filter="all" onclick="filter('all', this)">All</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="ICP" onclick="filter('ICP', this)">ICP</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="Positioning" onclick="filter('Positioning', this)">Positioning</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="GTM" onclick="filter('GTM', this)">GTM</button>
    </div>
    <div class="search-wrap">
      <input id="blogSearch" class="search-input" type="search" placeholder="Search posts" oninput="search(this.value)">
      <span class="search-icon">⌕</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="blog-main">
  <div class="bm-inner inner">
    {% if featuredPost %}
    <div class="featured-post" data-category="{{ featuredPost.data.category or 'GTM' }}">
      <a class="fp-card" href="{{ featuredPost.url }}">
        <div class="fp-badge">Featured</div>
        <h2 class="fp-title">{{ featuredPost.data.title }}</h2>
        <p class="fp-excerpt">{{ featuredPost.data.description }}</p>
        <div class="fp-meta">{{ featuredPost.date | postDate }} · {{ featuredPost.content | readingTime }}</div>
      </a>
      <div class="fp-side">
        <div class="fp-side-card">
          <strong>Want a custom diagnosis?</strong>
          <p>Run the 9-question assessment and identify your primary GTM bottleneck.</p>
          <a href="/assessment/">Run assessment →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="post-grid" id="postGrid">
      {% set count = 0 %}
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
        {% if not post.data.featured %}
        {% set count = count + 1 %}
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-card" data-title="{{ post.data.title | lower }}" data-description="{{ (post.data.description or '') | lower }}" data-category="{{ post.data.category or 'GTM' }}">
          <div class="fp-badge">{{ post.data.category or 'GTM' }}</div>
          <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
          <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          <div class="fp-meta">{{ post.date | postDate }} · {{ post.content | readingTime }}</div>
        </a>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}

      {% if count < 4 %}
      <article class="post-card placeholder" data-category="placeholder">
        <div class="fp-badge">Coming next</div>
        <h3>How to segment by buyer state</h3>
        <p>A practical model for changing messaging as intent matures.</p>
        <div class="fp-meta">Draft preview</div>
      </article>
      {% endif %}
      {% if count < 3 %}
      <article class="post-card placeholder" data-category="placeholder">
        <div class="fp-badge">Coming next</div>
        <h3>Signal quality in outbound systems</h3>
        <p>Where targeting logic breaks before SDRs ever touch a lead.</p>
        <div class="fp-meta">Draft preview</div>
      </article>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    <div class="bottom-layout">
      <div class="bottom-posts">
        <h3>Continue reading</h3>
        <ul>
          {% for post in collections.posts %}
          <li><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></li>
          {% endfor %}
          {% if collections.posts | length < 4 %}
          <li><span>Diagnostic scoring methodology (placeholder)</span></li>
          {% endif %}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <aside class="sidebar-cta">
        <p class="sc-kicker">Free diagnostic</p>
        <h4 class="sc-title">Name the GTM bottleneck before your next sprint.</h4>
        <p class="sc-body">Nine questions, four minutes, instant archetype + bottleneck output.</p>
        <a class="sc-btn" href="/assessment/">Run the assessment</a>
        <form class="sc-email-form" onsubmit="submitSidebar(event)">
          <label for="sc-email">Get new essays</label>
          <input id="sc-email" type="email" placeholder="you@company.com" required>
          <button type="submit">Notify me</button>
        </form>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
